{"tid":1765918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民〈公安條例〉修定撮要","createTime":"2019-12-02T08:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T11:12:00.000Z","uid":307270,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"df559fbee8fe71049a054b03a50f6458b7dd148a","tid":1765918,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"現時公安條例係喺1967年定立嘅，有關「暴動」同「非法集結」嘅定義完全outdated哂，又唔合符國際人權標準，亦違背基本法27條 Freedom of assembly。 令到「現場」只要有3個人做出威嚇性行為，旁邊嘅所有人就會被株埋9族，加上「現場」嘅 Area 定義無限遠，好似理大附近嘅尖東同何文田街道都當埋喺現場。。。所以搞到黑警可以無差別咁周圍濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實合時嘅法例，應該同犯上嘅罪行匹配，例如傷左人咪判傷人罪囉，而唔可以用空泛含糊嘅形容詞囊括所有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區諾軒參考左英國1986年嘅公安法，降低刑期（非法集結罪- 最高刑期降至6個月，暴動罪 - 降至3年），增加集結人數 (from 3 -&gt;12)，廢除「破壞社會安寧」作為控罪，改為「使用暴力及威脅使用暴力，另外提倡加入有冇「共同目的」嚟做判斷。<br />\n<br />\n雖然草案已獲律政司發出證明書，不過都要經林奠同意，先可以放上立法會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(Reference: 直播 - 區諾軒朱凱廸提私人草案記者會 2019.12.02)"},{"pid":"81ff8dea8263b5c397c69a85c7a2c36a212880b0","tid":1765918,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20596c7514e082f002e78be2ca9380cfadcc4d4d","tid":1765918,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:20:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接廢除暴動罪"},{"pid":"9d54c5938c91368069f865b6d868657ff4fb628e","tid":1765918,"uid":307270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score